          "[SRL Processes as Identified by FOMM]",
          "The SRL processes were identified and mapped according to COPES. ",
          "Expectation-Maximization",
          "-",
          "3",
          "Cluster 1: Read First, Write Next: - 91 members: Reads materials first and then starts composing essays. They rarely go back to read the instructions. These ere the ones that performed better (even if slightly).\n\nCluster 2: Read and Write Simultaneously - 48 members:  Tended to alternatte more often between reading description and writing materials (to make sure).\n\nCluster 3: Reading with Quiz: Reads materials with intention of passing on the Quiz.",
          "Encouraging learners to Read First and Write next mildly promote the development of knowledge transfer. ",
